commit_message:
Use NoDBTestCase instead of TestCase (Part 9)

No need to use TestCase since it will use DB fixture.
This patch updates below test case in unit/api/openstack/test_common.py:
class LimiterTest(test.TestCase)
class SortParamUtilsTest(test.TestCase)
class PaginationParamsTest(test.TestCase)

The follow class still keeps to use test.TestCase
class MiscFunctionsTest(test.TestCase)

For common.check_img_metadata_properties_quota call db API.

Change-Id: I9ca20c85d54af50897bb8add89b010f8c5867525
Signed-off-by: ShaoHe Feng <shaohe.feng@intel.com>
